{"tid":680494,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"想問點解呢兩日多左咁多猁狗","createTime":"2018-05-27T08:37:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T10:44:07.000Z","uid":40348,"like":32,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"8f197dd145e9a1b77da11d2274185d581dd59ce6","tid":680494,"uid":40348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T08:37:41.000Z","msg":"身為皇迷<br />\n都覺得對面傷左沙拿好可惜<br />\n<br />\n但個個話拉膠鎖沙拉既睇一睇圖<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/27/163151_098262797626fd11ca8a6679648c1689.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2F163151_098262797626fd11ca8a6679648c1689.png&h=a7a7c083&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢張圖明顯沙拿未跌前就扣住拉膠<br />\n到底邊個鎖邊個？<br />\n<br />\n同埋猁記頭20分鐘逼搶係打得好好<br />\n<br />\n打到皇馬半場都過唔到<br />\n但有踢波既你自己都知逼搶逼得幾耐<br />\n<br />\n個個無限氣咩<br />\n<br />\nBtw 可能最近5界拎左4次冠軍<br />\n好小睇到其他隊拎冠<br />\n<br />\n想問下有邊次拎歐聯冠軍係無人屌黑哨嫁<br />\n真心問"},{"pid":"706aa47af9ad6dbd1ef3cfb58787e6e992fea744","tid":680494,"uid":40348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T04:46:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9d788a9aa5aa65ef98eacdca098d88391eebb5f","tid":680494,"uid":131369,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T04:49:53.000Z","msg":"好多疤迷黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"592ca9a473a852c98c13421ebacccc928018d684","tid":680494,"uid":4496,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T04:53:48.000Z","msg":"垃圾痢狗怨婦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75a58c4014c95eef7dbfb67c87b49c9d702f7a96","tid":680494,"uid":10757,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b9d788a9aa5aa65ef98eacdca098d88391eebb5f","tid":680494,"uid":131369,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T04:49:53.000Z","msg":"好多疤迷黎<img src=\"/as